	<tag id="ID_SAVE_BUTTON_DIALOG"><![CDATA[This is the Save Game button.  If you click on this, your current game progress is saved, and when you come back you will still have all the tools and clues you've collected so far.]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_SAVED_DIALOG"><![CDATA[Game Saved.]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_SCROLL_DIALOG"><![CDATA[This button controls whether the scroll lock is on.  If scroll lock is OFF, you need to hold SHIFT and move the mouse to navigate around the wider rooms.  If scroll lock is ON, you just need to move the mouse around and the screen will move with you.]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_MUSIC_DIALOG"><![CDATA[This button controls whether the background music is playing.]]></tag>
	
